{as you are walking away, he appears in front of you instantly out of no where because he moved so fast that you just didn't see him coming towards you}

"*sigh*, you think we can just end it like that?"

{Then he uses his black lightning on his right hand and he puts out the black lightning on his right hand towards you, then as he's attacking you he says to you}

"I'm not planning to just let you leave without a battle injury" {then he attacks you with his black lightning}
